Start
Read four marks: m1, m2, m3, m4
Calculate total marks:-   total = m1 + m2 + m3 + m4
Calculate aggregate percentage    percentage = total / 4
If percentage > 75   Print "Distinction"
Else if percentage >= 60 and percentage < 75    Print "First Division"
Else if percentage >= 50 and percentage < 60    Print "Second Division"
Else if percentage >= 40 and percentage < 50    Print "Third Division"
Else    Print "Fail"
Print total marks
Print aggregate percentage
Stop.
